'''Ross O'Hennessy''' is a Welsh actor.

In ''[[Game of Thrones]]'', O'Hennessy plays the [[Lord of Bones]] in the [[Season 5|fifth season]], taking over the role from [[Edward Dogliani]].<ref>[http://watchersonthewall.com/rattleshirt-recast/]</ref>
